text: trong ban bangkeut mekh cheachraen chean daoy kmean sasar del puok anak meulkheunh vea . haey trong ban baoh phnom cheachraen cheab now leu phendei daembi komaoy vea ronhchuoy dl puok anak . haey trong ban pongreay satv krob braphet now leu vea . haey yeung ban banhchouh tukaphlieng pileu mekh ruoch yeung ban bandoh roukkhcheate krob braphet da srasabamprong now leu vea
